description: RavenQuest BioMed Inc., a cannabis company, focuses on the cannabis production, management services and consulting, and specialized research and development activities. The company operates in two segments, Consulting Business, and Cultivation and Sale of Medical Cannabis. It offers its products under the Lore Cannabis and Bloomera brand names. The company was formerly known as Ravencrest Resources Inc. and changed its name to RavenQuest BioMed Inc. in September 2017. RavenQuest BioMed Inc. was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
